---
import BaseHead from '../components/BaseHead.astro';
import Header from '../components/Header.astro';
import Footer from '../components/Footer.astro';
---
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <BaseHead title="About | Circle of Life" description="About Circle of Life" />
</head>
<body>
  <Header />
  <main>
    <h1>About Circle of Life</h1>
    <p>
      Half my life is mirrored in the River Cam; the other half is pinned to a lab whiteboard
      bristling with <mark class="yellow">untested hypotheses</mark>.
      Having turned a <span class="red-box">Cambridge PhD</span> into a lifestyle,
      I've found that clinical trial data reads better than most novels.
      I'm still here — mostly because the questions remain far more seductive than the answers.
    </p>
    <p>
      Circle of Life exists because I found existing biotech content either too shallow
      or too fragmented — no platform offered <em>expert-level analysis</em> from
      someone inside the lab, with multidisciplinary insights in both Chinese and English.
    </p>

    <h2>What I Cover</h2>
    <ul>
      <li>🫀 <strong>Metabolic & Liver Disease</strong>: MASH/MASLD, GLP-1 applications, novel targets</li>
      <li>🧠 <strong>Neuroscience</strong>: Brain-computer interfaces, neurodegeneration, neuromodulation</li>
      <li>💊 <strong>Drug Pipelines</strong>: FDA decisions, clinical data readouts, industry dynamics</li>
      <li>🔬 <strong>Longevity Biology</strong>: Senolytics, epigenetic reprogramming, aging clocks</li>
    </ul>

    <h2>My Philosophy</h2>
    <p>
      Hot topics have many interpreters. My edge is a <strong>researcher's skepticism</strong>:
      I'll tell you when a "breakthrough" is overhyped, which targets are undervalued,
      and what the data actually says versus what the press release claims.
    </p>

    <h2>Get in Touch</h2>
    <p>
      Reach me via <a href="mailto:cherubholmes@gmail.com">email</a>.
      I welcome collaborations, guest perspectives, and reader questions.
    </p>
  </main>
  <Footer />
</body>
</html>

<style>
h1 { margin-bottom: 1.5rem; }
ul { padding-left: 1.2rem; }
ul li { margin-bottom: 0.6rem; }

mark.yellow {
  background: #F7E623;
  color: #000;
  padding: 0 0.15em;
  font-style: normal;
}

.red-box {
  display: inline-block;
  background: transparent;
  color: #000;
  border: 2.5px solid #EF5B5B;
  box-shadow: 3px 3px 0 #EF5B5B;
  padding: 0 0.35em;
  font-family: 'Archivo Black', sans-serif;
  font-size: 0.95em;
  letter-spacing: 0.02em;
  transform: rotate(-0.8deg);
  display: inline-block;
}
</style>
